column6: 1)/>! How might I be of service?

column3: That strange girl you met in the Empty is in our custody.
Her location is a closely guarded secret
column4: and she is being monitored night and day for any changes in her condition.

column3: We have also been treating any information regarding your mission as strictly confidential. It would cause quite a stir amongst the peoples of Norvrandt were it to become public knowledge
column4: and we cannot afford for anyone to interfere with our work.
the majority of the tasks we perform─such as delivering supplies and equipment─tend to go unnoticed for the most part. In order to maintain this status quo
column5: I and my colleagues will continue to lend our support in as discreet a manner as possible.
